Description: Configure the FreedomBox environment
 Installing FreedomBox changes your Debian system in many important
 ways. This includes installing a firewall and regenerating server
 certificates. It is therefore recommended that you install FreedomBox
 on a fresh Debian installation instead of an existing setup.
